NELSON EDDY AND JON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Re "Like Father, Like Son" (Morning Report, June 24): Check any legitimate 
biography or legitimate Hollywood source, and you will see that singer Nelson 
Eddy had no children, let alone a son named Jon who sings his "father's" old 
songs. This appears to be another Hollywood impostor, trying to cash in on a 
deceased star's fame. 
</P>
