<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOLIDAY WEEKEND 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Monday is Independence Day, the 218th anniversary of the adoption of the 
Declaration of Independence. Monday is observed as a federal holiday. Closed 
Monday: All government offices, courts, banks, post offices, stock and 
commodity exchanges, libraries and many businesses. MTA buses will follow 
Sunday schedules. 
</P>
