<P>
 World Cup soccer is finally here! Ex-East Coast goalie, SWF, 29, 5'9", trim, 
attractive, blue-eyed, multilingual, with a great sense of humor, seeks 
adventurous, spontaneous, athletic, tall, dark-haired, non-smoking gentleman, 
28-35, who equally enjoys soccer matches, foreign movies, wine, travel and 
fresh-air activities. MIKE DOWNEY 
