last year, finished first with 297.85 points in one-meter diving. Teammate 
Kristin Marguis was second with 289.40. 
</P>
<P>
 In boys' 16-18 one-meter diving, Tyce Rouston of Mission Viejo finished 
Friday's competition with 455.60 points. Tustin Dumas of Rose Bowl is first 
with 482.75 points. 
</P>
<P>
 Competition continues at 9 a.m. today in one- and three-meter diving. ERIK 
HAMILTON 
