Following the parade, the park located at 24933 Newhall Ave. will host an arts 
and crafts fair from noon to 4 p.m., featuring games, contests, arts and crafts 
and live entertainment, including the Santa Clarita Valley Concert Band, the 
Volunteers of Dixieland Fire Brigade and Joe Vento's Big Band Jazz All-Stars, 
but no fireworks. Admission is free, but there is a $2 entry fee for 
cake-decorating, pie-and bread-baking and vegetable-growing contests. 
Information: (805) 298-2787. 
