shows, concerts, fairs, military displays, barbecues and parades. The county 
Fire Department is operating a 24-hour recorded information line -- (714) 
834-4532 -- with details about public celebrations. There is also a hot line to 
report dangerous and illegal fireworks usage: (714) 538-3501. Where the 
festivities are and telephone numbers where available: 
