</P>
<P>
 * Banks and savings and loans will be closed. 
</P>
<P>
 * Schools, colleges and universities are closed Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 * Mail: There will be no postal service Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 * Trash: Trash will be collected one day late throughout the week, except in 
Anaheim and Orange, where the normal Tuesday schedule will be followed. 
</P>
<P>
 * Buses: OCTA buses will run on Sunday schedule Monday.  
